Sentencas: This paper describes the development of a computer model for simulating the transient operation of a tubular solid oxide fuel cell(SOFC).
Titulo: Transient modeling and simulation of a tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The model includes the electrochemical, thermal, and mass flow elements th;lt affect SOFC electrical output.
Titulo: Transient modeling and simulation of a tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The electrochemical and thermal parts of the model were developed and verified separately before they were combined to form the transient model.
Titulo: Transient modeling and simulation of a tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The results of model verification tests are presented.
Titulo: Transient modeling and simulation of a tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Transient simulations were conducted with constant reactant flows and constant inlet temperatures.
Titulo: Transient modeling and simulation of a tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The transient electrical response of the cell to a load change is described.
Titulo: Transient modeling and simulation of a tubular solid oxide fuel cell
